events.name: Boston College Eagles at Wake Forest Demon Deacons

headlines.description: Anthony Brown threw two of his career-high five touchdown passes to Jeff Smith, and Boston College beat Wake Forest 41-34 on Thursday night in a game that started two hours early with Hurricane Florence approaching.
headlines.shortLinkText: Brown throws 5 TDs, BC beats Wake Forest, 41-34

video.headline: BC's Smith is off to the races on long TD

events.name: Robert Morris Colonials at James Madison Dukes

headlines.description: Ben DiNucci accounted for a career-high five touchdowns and James Madison eased by Robert Morris 73-7 on Thursday night in a game played early because of Hurricane Florence.
headlines.shortLinkText: James Madison builds 52-0 halftime lead, beats Robert Morris

events.name: Tennessee Tech Golden Eagles at Utah State Aggies

headlines.description: Jordan Love was 21 of 26 for 236 yards and two touchdowns -- all in the first half -- and Utah State beat Tennessee Tech 73-12 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Utah State rushes for 7 TDs, cruises by Tennessee Tech 73-12
